  <brief_title>High Dose Inhaled Nitric Oxide for COVID-19 (ICU Patients)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of High Dose Inhaled Nitric Oxide in Intubated Patients Admitted With COVID-19</official_title>
  <sponsors>
